              "WarningsOrContraIndicationDescription": [
                {
                  "LanguageCode": "en",
                  "Value": "Do not use on damaged, inflamed, or bleeding skin. If you experience numbness or tingling, remove the support immediately and check that you are wearing the right size. Do not wear the support for long periods of time (no longer than 2 hours continuously, or 6 hours a day) and do not wear it while sleeping. Do not use the product in combination with other compression products, creams, skin oil, etc. Discontinue use if the support is no longer sufficiently elastic."
